<span style="background-color: #ffffff; color: #c8266a; font-size: 12pt;">SHIPPING AND DELIVERY</span></span></strong>﻿</strong></span></h2></div><div class="rte"><h2 class="yiv1476140631rte" style="right: auto;">&nbsp;</h2><div class="yiv1476140631rte" style="right: auto;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"><strong>How can I check my order?</strong></span></div><div class="yiv1476140631rte" style="right: auto;"><br><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">After your payment’s been verified, you will receive an email informing you that your order’s in the midst of preparation for delivery. Once it’s been shipped out from our Warehouse, you’ll receive an email notification as well. To check on your order status, do log in to your account and view ‘History and details of your orders’.</span></div><div class="yiv1476140631rte" style="right: auto;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span></div><div class="yiv1476140631rte" style="right: auto;"><br><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"><strong>Local Delivery:</strong></span></div><div class="yiv1476140631rte" style="right: auto;"><br><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">Once you placed and paid for your order, your item(s) will reach you 3-7 working days (excluding Weekends &amp; Public Holidays) after it have been dispatched from our Warehouse. You may either opt for normal or courier postage when checking out.</span></div><div class="yiv1476140631rte" style="right: auto;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span></div><div class="yiv1476140631rte" style="right: auto;"><br><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; text-decoration: underline;">i) Normal Delivery/ With Certificate of Posting (COP):</span></div><div class="yiv1476140631rte" style="right: auto;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span></div><div class="yiv1476140631rte" style="right: auto;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">The cost of normal delivery charges for local will be 'FREE' regardless of the weight and size of the items. Please note that order tracking is not available for normal postage deliveries and <strong>Boutique</strong> is not responsible for any lost of normal mails. Kindly wait 3-7 full working days for your orders to arrive. </span><br><br><br><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; text-decoration: underline;">ii) Courier Services:</span></div><div class="yiv1476140631rte" style="right: auto;"><br><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">The cost of courier service charges is priced at $4.00 per order for a maximum weight of up to 3kg. Please note that order tracking is not available for courier services. If you are not around to acknowledge the delivery of your parcel, the carrier will leave a calling card telling you how you can pick it up or arrange for another delivery for your convenience without any extra cost. Alternatively, you can <a href="http://www.ralfashion.com/estore/contact-form.php" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">contact</a> our Customer Care for your parcel details if you have any enquires.</span></div><div class="yiv1476140631rte" style="right: auto;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span></div><div class="yiv1476140631rte" style="right: auto;"><br><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"><strong>International Delivery:</strong></span></div><div class="yiv1476140631rte" style="right: auto;"><br><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">We ship all parcels via Singpost. To find out the cost of shipping to your country, simply sign up an account with us, add your desired items to the cart and use the fast and easy shipping calculator to receive a quote.</span></div><div class="yiv1476140631rte" style="right: auto;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span></div><div class="yiv1476140631rte" style="right: auto;"><br><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"><strong>Estimated Delivery Time:</strong></span></div><div class="yiv1476140631rte" style="right: auto;"><br><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">Malaysia &amp; Brunei: 3 - 6 Working Days.</span><br><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">Countries in Asia &amp; Pacific (Excluding Australia, New Zealand, Japan): 3 - 7 Working Days.</span><br><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">Other Countries: 4 - 10 Working Days.</span><br><br><br><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"><br></span><br /><span id="yui_3_2_0_21_133507089989280" style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">*All terms and conditions are subjected to change without prior notice*</span>